These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, peas
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, ship
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily
1. the person eating onion is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the ship is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Food      | peas     | onion |
| Transport   | ship | roller      |
| Flower         | lily    | poppy      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, october
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, mauve
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Flower         | rose      | daffodil |
| Birthday   | october | january    |
| Color           | mauve         | turquise         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, ritmeester
There are 2 different nationalities: german, japanese
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, mauve
1. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the german##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Cigar         | cain | ritmeester |
| Nationality         | japanese       | german       |
| Color   | mauve       | blue         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
