There 2 different types of food: tomato, peach
1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Flower    | dahlia    | tulip     |
| Birthday       | december    | july |
| Food   | tomato | peach    |

