.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, electronic
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, manager
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, february
1. the manager is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the musician is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Music-Genre       | electronic | indie |
| Job         | musician      | manager  |
| Birthday   | november | february   |

