.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-7::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, azure
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, tomato
2 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish
1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |       2       |
| Color       | aquamarine   | azure     |
| Food       | cranberry   | tomato |
| Pet   | hamster | goldfish        |

