2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | iced-tea   |
| Game   | bridge          | whist   |
| Hobby         | dancing     | singing |

 